'''Global Jurist''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[law review|journal]] of legal scholarship. It focuses on [[comparative law]], [[international law]], [[law and economics]], [[law and development]] and [[legal anthropology]]. Global Jurist favors a critical non-ethnocentric approach. It publishes articles in English Spanish and French.
